    {
      "slide": 3,
      "title": "研究背景：PD-L1 TPS 仍需补充解释",
      "layout": "content",
      "visual_intent": "quiet explanatory slide, no source panels",
      "source_boundary": "mixed",
      "text_items": [
        {
          "role": "title",
          "text": "研究背景：PD-L1 TPS 仍需要补充解释",
          "bbox": [
            0.045,
            0.108,
            0.58,
            0.09
          ],
          "font_size": 40,
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#07143d",
          "wrap": false
        },
        {
          "role": "body",
          "text": "肺癌仍是全球高负担恶性肿瘤，\nPD-1/PD-L1 抑制剂已成为 NSCLC 重要治疗方案。",
          "bbox": [
            0.142,
            0.295,
            0.48,
            0.12
          ],
          "font_size": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#07143d",
          "wrap": true
        },
        {
          "role": "body",
          "text": "PD-L1 TPS 是常用预测标志物，\n但预测准确性有限：部分 TPS<1% 患者仍可能获益，\n部分 TPS≥50% 患者无应答。",
          "bbox": [
            0.142,
            0.485,
            0.5,
            0.18
          ],
          "font_size": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#07143d",
          "wrap": true
        },
        {
          "role": "body",
          "text": "肠道微生物组可调控宿主免疫状态，\n可能为 TPS 分层提供补充解释。",
          "bbox": [
            0.142,
            0.735,
            0.46,
            0.12
          ],
          "font_size": 22,
          "bold": false,
          "color": "#07143d",
          "wrap": true
        }
      ],
      "speaker_notes": "",
      "source_layers": []
    },
