      "slide": 6,
      "title": "结果一：TPS<1% 组多样性与均匀度偏低",
      "layout": "figure-first",
      "visual_intent": "wide alpha diversity panel dominates slide",
      "source_boundary": "grep_required",
      "text_items": [
        {
          "role": "title",
          "text": "结果一：TPS<1% 组\n多样性与均匀度偏低",
          "bbox": [
            0.05,
            0.1,
            0.35,
            0.14
          ],
          "font_size": 30,
          "bold": true,
          "color": "#07143d",
          "wrap": true
        },
        {
          "role": "body",
          "text": "α 多样性：Pielou 均匀度三组差异显著，TPS<1% 组为 0.52±0.14，低于另外两组。\n\nβ 多样性：Bray-Curtis PCoA 显示组间结构差异，PERMANOVA p=0.008，R²=0.068。\n\n含义：PD-L1 阴性患者可能存在更明显的肠道生态失衡。",
          "bbox": [
            0.07,
            0.3,
            0.34,
            0.46
          ],
